  "detailed_description": "The story takes place in a continent where war has suddenly broken out, and the southern kingdom of Astrand has suffered an invasion by the neighboring country of Dane.<br>In order to save the country from extinction, the protagonist group embarks on a journey to travel the world ......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/30427201de13ad8334aa12a0cbc6ee16.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/30427201de13ad8334aa12a0cbc6ee16.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/30427201de13ad8334aa12a0cbc6ee16.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>  <br>This game is full of strategic battles that require players to test their patience and strategy.<br>This game is full of strategic battles that require players to test their patience and strategy, and requires players to make good use of various favorable terrain environments to fight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/f4e4316f538fcf7d42871049dea7195b.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/f4e4316f538fcf7d42871049dea7195b.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/f4e4316f538fcf7d42871049dea7195b.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A multi-player team of distinctive characters.<br>Each character has multiple unique skills, and utilizing the skills of each character is the key to this game.<br>Players can enjoy a challenging and strategic game.<br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/923ec56086a169fa2ceda3f5809f253c.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/923ec56086a169fa2ceda3f5809f253c.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/923ec56086a169fa2ceda3f5809f253c.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features an “Inn” where you can store and enhance your character's equipment or weapons to improve their strength.<br><br>Whether you win a normal battle or a battle with special conditions, you can enjoy the fun of this game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/686d20e82ebe4b44410eef746c9465db.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/686d20e82ebe4b44410eef746c9465db.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/686d20e82ebe4b44410eef746c9465db.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The story takes place in a continent where war has suddenly broken out, and the southern kingdom of Astrand has suffered an invasion by the neighboring country of Dane.<br>In order to save the country from extinction, the protagonist group embarks on a journey to travel the world ......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/30427201de13ad8334aa12a0cbc6ee16.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/30427201de13ad8334aa12a0cbc6ee16.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/30427201de13ad8334aa12a0cbc6ee16.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>  <br>This game is full of strategic battles that require players to test their patience and strategy.<br>This game is full of strategic battles that require players to test their patience and strategy, and requires players to make good use of various favorable terrain environments to fight.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/f4e4316f538fcf7d42871049dea7195b.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/f4e4316f538fcf7d42871049dea7195b.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/f4e4316f538fcf7d42871049dea7195b.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A multi-player team of distinctive characters.<br>Each character has multiple unique skills, and utilizing the skills of each character is the key to this game.<br>Players can enjoy a challenging and strategic game.<br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/923ec56086a169fa2ceda3f5809f253c.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/923ec56086a169fa2ceda3f5809f253c.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/923ec56086a169fa2ceda3f5809f253c.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features an “Inn” where you can store and enhance your character's equipment or weapons to improve their strength.<br><br>Whether you win a normal battle or a battle with special conditions, you can enjoy the fun of this game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/686d20e82ebe4b44410eef746c9465db.poster.avif?t=1729735147\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/686d20e82ebe4b44410eef746c9465db.webm?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164820/extras/686d20e82ebe4b44410eef746c9465db.mp4?t=1729735147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
